Installation Instructions

For a first-time build, run these commands to generate the makefiles and then
build the binaries.

    $ tar xzf vitapi-1.0.0.tar.gz
    $ cd vitapi-1.0.0
    $ cmake .
    $ make
    $ make test
    $ sudo make install

Note that you will need cmake (www.cmake.org) installed in order to build the
software.  You'll like it.

---
